+ Parameters

    + object (optional, int) ... `POST` | `PUT` only: `1` to retrieve the user object, `0` (default) to retrieve the token only
    + settings (optional, int) ... `1` to retrieve user settings with the user object in a sub-property `settings` (requires `object=1`), `0` (default) to skip returning the settings

